  "text": "In the recent years, many researchers have used the theory of Compressed Sensing or Compressive Sampling (CS) for their field of study. Candes and his colleagues in [CITATION_1] and Donoho in [CITATION_2] proposed this theory and it has been served in some applications such as image processing [CITATION_3] ,radar [CITATION_4] , signal detection [CITATION_5] and other applications [CITATION_6] .",
